        Parameters:
        loggingEntityLength - Maximum length of HTTP request before truncation.

      • getMaxRetries

      • setMaxRetries

        public void setMaxRetries(int maxRetries)
        Sets the maximum number of retries for any retryable errors. Retry will automatically happen on any request that is marked as retriable. Setting this to 0 disables retries. Defaults to 3.
        Parameters:
        maxRetries - Maximum number of retries.

        public void setIgnoreCertificates(boolean ignoreCertificates)
